p_20104_ca_20833.name: Fleece
p_20104_ca_20833.description: Midweight recycled Polartec® 300 series fleece features durable water repellent finish at exterior.
p_20104_ca_20833.tooltip: Midweight recycled Polartec® 300 series fleece features durable water repellent finish at exterior.

p_20104_ca_20834.name: Taslan
p_20104_ca_20834.description: Abrasion-resistant fabric at shoulders, chest and elbows aids with durability in high-stress areas as with pack-carry.
p_20104_ca_20834.tooltip: Abrasion-resistant fabric at shoulders, chest and elbows aids with durability in high-stress areas as with pack-carry.

p_20104_ca_20835.name: Zippers
p_20104_ca_20835.description: The teeth part of the zipper on the jacket includes everything except the zipper handle itself. YKK® zipper.
p_20104_ca_20835.tooltip: The teeth part of the zipper on the jacket includes everything except the zipper handle itself. YKK® zipper.

p_20104_ca_20836.name: Zipper Pulls
p_20104_ca_20836.description: The handle part of the zipper you hold to move the slider up or down, to zip or unzip your jacket. YKK® zipper.
p_20104_ca_20836.tooltip: The handle part of the zipper you hold to move the slider up or down, to zip or unzip your jacket. YKK® zipper.

p_20104_ca_20837.name: Logo Stitching
p_20104_ca_20837.description: Embroidery color of The North Face® logo on the front left chest and back right shoulder.
p_20104_ca_20837.tooltip: Embroidery color of The North Face® logo on the front left chest and back right shoulder.

p_20104_ca_21346.name: Custom Label
p_20104_ca_21346.description: Enter the text for the interior custom label.  Labels are limited to a 15-character max and are printed on the interior back near the hangtag.  Labels are printed in the same color as the logo stitching.
